### 1. Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Authorization: Bearer {{YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE}}

### 2. Get User by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{USER_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE}}

### 3. Update User
PUT {{baseUrl}}/{{USER_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE}}
Content-Type: application/json

